    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>诸神陨落，金雾弥漫</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在诸神和外神的史诗大战后，所有神明陨落，他们的鲜血化为金雾席卷大地，侵蚀生物的灵魂，使其陷入无尽的疯狂和变异。在漫天的金雾之下，只残留少数还保留神智的人类，在各个残存的避难处苟延残喘，保留着一丝文明的火种。幸运的是，一名神秘的少女——露出现于世间，她找到死去的英雄，赐予他们不朽的肉体，这些复活的英雄们被称为猎金人。在露的指引下，猎金人前往各处险地，猎杀被金蚀的怪物获取流金，用来修复破损的命运之网，为停滞在末日中的世界带来新的希望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282300/extras/278141e74e5054e5b01e4ac462e20344.poster.avif?t=1770999878\" width=700 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282300/extras/278141e74e5054e5b01e4ac462e20344.webm?t=1770999878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282300/extras/278141e74e5054e5b01e4ac462e20344.mp4?t=1770999878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>剑与魔法，动作战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏以第三人称视角，呈现流畅无比的动作表现。并引入“瞄准”机制，在传统动作战斗的基础上丰富操作维度。尽情运用多种多样的连招，精准打击敌人的弱点，与队友默契配合，战胜拦路的敌人吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282300/extras/06f513ea21d8af03b79ca6f9cc0b6067.poster.avif?t=1770999878\" width=700 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282300/extras/06f513ea21d8af03b79ca6f9cc0b6067.webm?t=1770999878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282300/extras/06f513ea21d8af03b79ca6f9cc0b6067.mp4?t=1770999878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富职业，定制流派</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >佣兵、巫师、黑箭、影枭、先知，5种不同职业待你体验！每个职业都有独一无二的武器装备及特性，并可在两种武器或战斗流派中自由切换。选定你的职业和流派，在十余种技能中精心挑选，合理搭配天赋，组成强力Build。收集高级装备，提升词缀等级，解锁强力被动，让你的Build更上一层楼！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282300/extras/1dd34317e54bcff42836c8e7460395f8.poster.avif?t=1770999878\" width=700 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282300/extras/1dd34317e54bcff42836c8e7460395f8.webm?t=1770999878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282300/extras/1dd34317e54bcff42836c8e7460395f8.mp4?t=1770999878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>定位搭配，组队作战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为猎金人，你可以单枪匹马，或与最多两位队友并肩作战。在残酷的迷雾之中，没有所谓的英雄，只有你死我亡的战斗。和队友选择不同的职业，进行战术搭配，可以大大提升你们的作战能力和撤离几率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282300/extras/379860d86fa06b4c5983b92573360959.poster.avif?t=1770999878\" width=700 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282300/extras/379860d86fa06b4c5983b92573360959.webm?t=1770999878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282300/extras/379860d86fa06b4c5983b92573360959.mp4?t=1770999878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>寻宝探险，逃出生天</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里有珍贵的流金和无尽的战利品，但你必须要消灭一切拦路的敌人——无论是恐怖的锈蚀者还是阴险无情的同行。每场战斗你都将压上一切赌注，一旦丧命就会掉落所有的装备。找到归返林精并杀出重围，才能回到温暖的营地。成为猎人还是猎物？一切取决于你的选择！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282300/extras/6bf58333866e92ccb7dd71d339f97f36.poster.avif?t=1770999878\" width=700 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282300/extras/6bf58333866e92ccb7dd71d339f97f36.webm?t=1770999878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282300/extras/6bf58333866e92ccb7dd71d339f97f36.mp4?t=1770999878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
